com.google.gwt.core.client.impl
Class LoadingStrategyBase.RequestData

java.lang.Object
  com.google.gwt.core.client.impl.LoadingStrategyBase.RequestData
Enclosing class:
LoadingStrategyBase
protected static class LoadingStrategyBase.RequestData
extends java.lang.Object

Since LoadingStrategy must support concurrent requests, we keep most of the relevant info in the RequestData, and pass it around. Once created, a RequestData interacts primarily with it's DownloadStrategy, which will attempt call out to the RequestData's tryInstall function if the download succeeds, or it's onLoadError if the download fails.
